window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Kiran is caught in world of gods, time magic, and troublesome clans bent on his destruction. But with danger comes opportunity: the chance to truly grow as a cultivator and grab the power to control his own destiny.</p> <p>For fans of the Cradle, A Thousand Li, and Heaven's Laws series, this epic progression fantasy story is a western cultivation fantasy novel with mild romance but no harem.</p>"; 
